  <h2>
    <span class="">以下豆列推荐</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;
      <span class="pl">&nbsp;(
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/3320907/doulists">全部</a>
        ) </span>

  </h2>


    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/211611/" target="_blank">豆瓣读过少于100人，但确值得推荐的书</a>
                <span class="pl">(座头鲸赫连么么)</span>
            </li>
